comments: Hart (NOP) maintains a legal guarding position through the dribble hand-off and cleanly dislodges the ball from Young (CHI).
Young (CHI) makes contact with Hayes' (NOP) wrist during his shooting motion that affects his shot near the rim.
Young (CHI) take two legal steps after the gather.
During the rebound, Temple (CHI) tries to dislodge the ball from Williamson (NOP) and marginal contact occurs to his arm that does not affect his ability to maintain control of the ball.
Carter Jr. (CHI) jumps forward and makes contact to Williamson's (NOP) arm and affects his driving shot attempt.
During the rebound, Carter Jr. (CHI) and Williamson (NOP) engage and disengage and the contact is marginal.
Hart (NOP) does not make contact to Carter's (CHI) arm on the put-back shot attempt.
During the inbound, Redick (NOP) disengages from Temple (CHI) as he approaches Williamson's (NOP) screen and the contact is marginal.
After the rebound, Hart (NOP) tries to steal the ball and marginal contact occurs to Carter Jr.'s (CHI) arm that does not affect his ability to make his intended pass.
Bledsoe (NOP) moves laterally into White's (CHI) path and makes contact to his body that affects his SQBR.
Hart (NOP) maintains a legal guarding position on LaVine (CHI) and cleanly dislodges the ball out of bounds.
LaVine (CHI) lifts and re-plants his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Hart (NOP) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by LaVine (CHI).
White (CHI) makes contact with Bledsoe's (NOP) arm during his upward shooting motion that affects his jump shot attempt.
Williamson (NOP) makes marginal leg to leg contact as White (CHI) slips past the contact and makes the pass.
LaVine (CHI) lifts and re-plants his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Hart (NOP) commits a take foul on Young (CHI).
Hart (NOP) commits a take foul on LaVine (CHI).
Williamson (NOP) establishes himself in a screening position in LaVine's (CHI) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
LaVine (CHI) makes contact with Ingram's (NOP) body after the release and affects his ability to follow-through naturally on his jump shot attempt.
LaVine (CHI) does not step out of bounds and keeps his heel elevated above the boundary line during his drive.
Hayes (NOP) commits a take foul on LaVine (CHI).
Ingram (NOP) commits a take foul on White (CHI).
